en_724935_0	The Army was among different state and private sector agencies that put up a separate stall for recruitment of new soldiers during the government’s ‘Government Service to the Village’ project that took place on Saturday (1) in Matale District.
en_724935_1	The stall at Sangamitta College premises, erected by troops of the 11 Division Headquarters under command to the Security Force Headquarters - Central (SFHQ-Cen) was supported by the Mechanized Infantry Regiment, Directorate of Personnel Administration, Directorate of Pay & Records and Directorate of Recruitment.
en_724935_2	Several Senior Officers, Officers and Other Ranks attended the occasion.
